<lb ed="C I" n="0158a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>靜明等修塔造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之一　碑陰" type="其他"/><head>之一　碑陰</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a01"/><p id="pI01p0158a0101">蓋玄宗凝湛。至道沖<note n="0158001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30933;＝煥【史】</note><app n="0158001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">煥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30933;</rdg></app>。既
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a02"/>幽且<note n="0158002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30835;＝遠【史】</note><app n="0158002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30835;</rdg></app>。似滅如存。雖復天
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a03"/><note n="0158003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30934;＝旋【史】</note><app n="0158003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30934;</rdg></app>地遊。不究空<note n="0158004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30587;＝寂【史】</note><app n="0158004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30587;</rdg></app>之境。日
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a04"/>住月來。詎盡微妙之域。至
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a05"/>於出入四生。迴<note n="0158005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30935;＝還【史】</note><app n="0158005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">還</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30935;</rdg></app>六道。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a06"/>不<note n="0158006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30936;＝顧【史】</note><app n="0158006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顧</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30936;</rdg></app>己愛身。視陰昔日。智
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a07"/>惠莫之留。神力不能保。而
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a08"/>大慈應世。法輪既轉。群生
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a09"/>於是迴向。庶類所以歸依。
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a10"/>智禪師弟子靜明。知生生
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a11"/>之非有覺滅滅之為空。思
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a12"/>運己於法<note n="0158007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11971;＝船【史】</note><app n="0158007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">船</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11971;</rdg></app>。欲<note n="0158008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30937;＝澡【史】</note><app n="0158008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">澡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30937;</rdg></app>心於正
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a13"/>水。以大齊天保八年歲次
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a14"/>丁丑十一月廿九日。<note n="0158009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30938;＝勸【史】</note><app n="0158009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30938;</rdg></app>化
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a15"/>邑義等。脩孫<note n="0158010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30939;＝崗【史】</note><app n="0158010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">崗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30939;</rdg></app>上故塔并
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a16"/>石象一區。嵩山帶其左。神
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a17"/>堆挾其右。南<note n="0158011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30940;＝望【史】</note><app n="0158011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30940;</rdg></app>脩嶺。北眺
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a18"/>萇河。擢茲勝地。建此良因。
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a19"/>於是名僧慕義。上德依仁。
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a20"/>庶以此福。普及群生。使國
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a21"/>祚大康。世業永固。合邑諸
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a22"/>人。俱昇寶舟。同濟彼岸。年
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a23"/>住如流。時事焉屬。唯刊与
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a24"/>石。永為不朽。　其詞曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a25"/>神宗無極。空<app source="0158004" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30587;</rdg></app>難元。唯見
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a26"/>生滅。交互相翻。仁師<app source="0158002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30835;</rdg></app>識。
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a27"/>建此良因。東西勸化。邑義
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a28"/>同津。脩營故塔。宛麗初新。
<lb ed="C I" n="0158a29"/>寶舟共汎。捨偽歸真。</p>
